      "text": "Around a third of the world's population will own one."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 11110.0,
      "end_time": 14040.0,
      "text": "Smartphones touch every element of our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14040.0,
      "end_time": 16560.0,
      "text": "But did you know that they also connect nearly every"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
