      "text": "element on the planetï¼Ÿ"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18460.0,
      "end_time": 22270.0,
      "text": "In fact, of the 118 elements on the periodic table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 22270.0,
