      "text": "These raw materials are extracted from the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 28780.0,
      "end_time": 30680.0,
      "text": "and shipped to refineries and factories"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 30680.0,
      "end_time": 32563.0,
      "text": "in a truly global supply chain."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 34740.0,
      "end_time": 35690.0,
      "text": "Silicon."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 35690.0,
      "end_time": 38250.0,
      "text": "One of the most common elements in the earth's crust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38250.0,
      "end_time": 40890.0,
      "text": "is used to make the billions of transistors in the chips"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40890.0,
      "end_time": 42093.0,
      "text": "that power your phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 43650.0,
      "end_time": 45950.0,
      "text": "Gold is used for electrical wiring."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45950.0,
      "end_time": 48623.0,
      "text": "About 0.03 grams of it in each iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 50720.0,
      "end_time": 54133.0,
      "text": "Indium, another metal, is used to make touch screens."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55790.0,
      "end_time": 57420.0,
      "text": "But when it comes to batteries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 57420.0,
      "end_time": 59720.0,
      "text": "lithium is one of the key components,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59720.0,
      "end_time": 63430.0,
      "text": "and this element is only mined in a handful of countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 63430.0,
      "end_time": 67000.0,
      "text": "Until recently, Chile used to produce the most lithium."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 67000.0,
      "end_time": 69593.0,
      "text": "But now Australia has the biggest market share."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72470.0,
      "end_time": 74650.0,
      "text": "The Democratic Republic of Congo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74650.0,
      "end_time": 76420.0,
      "text": "a dangerously unstable country"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76420.0,
      "end_time": 78340.0,
      "text": "with a poor human rights record,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78340.0,
