    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 113870.0,
      "end_time": 115490.0,
      "text": "but they are hard to extract"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 115490.0,
      "end_time": 118253.0,
      "text": "without producing toxic and radioactive byproducts."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119460.0,
      "end_time": 121860.0,
      "text": "Many of the elements used in smartphones"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121860.0,
